name: Devola and Popola (Nier)
description:
This a lora trained on NAI on twins from the legendary series of Yoko Taro Nier. It's capable of generating them and retaining the facial features as well as clothing. You can swap out clothes freely and it is possible to generate the twins separate although it needs some fiddling. To call the LoRA use devola popola activation tag.

Hope you will enjoy using this lora as much as I did :D If you like what I'm doing and want to support me feel free to do so!
